    # Binary Search

    /**
 * @param {number[]} nums
 * @param {number} target
 * @return {number}
 */
var search = function(nums, target) {
    let start = 0
    let end = nums.length - 1

    while (start <= end) {
        mid = Math.floor((start + end) / 2)
        if (nums[mid] > target) {
            end = mid - 1
        }
        if (nums[mid] < target) {
            start = mid + 1
        }
        if(nums[mid] === target) return mid
    }
    return -1
};
